<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <title>Festival Reminder - Festival App</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    body, table, td, p, a, li, blockquote {
      -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
    }
    table, td {
      mso-table-lspace: 0pt;
      mso-table-rspace: 0pt;
    }
    img {
      -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
      border: 0;
      height: auto;
      line-height: 100%;
      outline: none;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0 !important;
      padding: 0 !important;
      background-color: #f4f4f7;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .email-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #f4f4f7;
      padding: 40px 0;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .email-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #6366f1 50%, #3b82f6 100%);
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .email-header h1 {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .email-header .logo {
      font-size: 64px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .countdown-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 8px 20px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 15px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }
    .email-body {
      padding: 40px;
    }
    .email-body h2 {
      color: #1f2937;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
    }
    .email-body p {
      color: #4b5563;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    }
    .button-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 5px;
    }
    .button-secondary {
      background: #e5e7eb;
      color: #374151 !important;
    }
    .festival-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ede9fe 0%, #ddd6fe 100%);
      border: 2px solid #8b5cf6;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .festival-name {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #5b21b6;
      margin: 0 0 15px 0;
    }
    .festival-location {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #7c3aed;
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
    }
    .festival-dates {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #6d28d9;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .checklist-section {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .checklist-title {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1f2937;
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
    }
    .checklist {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .checklist li {
      padding: 12px 0;
      padding-left: 35px;
      position: relative;
      color: #4b5563;
      font-size: 15px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .checklist li:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .checklist li:before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      border: 2px solid #d1d5db;
      border-radius: 4px;
      background: #ffffff;
    }
    .info-box {
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      border-left: 4px solid #6366f1;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    }
    .info-box p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #4b5563;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .excitement-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fde68a 100%);
      border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    }
    .excitement-box p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #92400e;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .email-footer {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 30px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .email-footer p {
      color: #9ca3af;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    }
    .email-footer a {
      color: #6366f1;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background-color: #e5e7eb;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .email-wrapper { padding: 20px 10px; }
      .email-header { padding: 30px 20px; }
      .email-header h1 { font-size: 26px; }
      .email-header .logo { font-size: 48px; }
      .email-body { padding: 30px 20px; }
      .email-footer { padding: 25px 20px; }
      .button { display: block; padding: 16px 24px; margin: 10px 0; }
      .festival-card { padding: 20px; }
      .festival-name { font-size: 24px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <div class="email-container">
            <!-- Header -->
            <div class="email-header">
              <div class="logo">&#127915;</div>
              <h1>C'est bientot le jour J !</h1>
              <div class="countdown-badge">&#9200; Plus que {{daysUntil}} jour(s) !</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Body -->
            <div class="email-body">
              <h2>Bonjour {{firstName}} !</h2>

              <p>Le festival approche a grands pas et nous avons hate de vous y retrouver ! Voici un rappel des informations importantes pour profiter au maximum de votre experience.</p>

              <!-- Festival Card -->
              <div class="festival-card">
                <h3 class="festival-name">{{festival.name}}</h3>
                <p class="festival-location">&#128205; {{festival.location}}</p>
                <p class="festival-dates">&#128197; {{festival.startDate}} - {{festival.endDate}}</p>
              </div>

              <div class="excitement-box">
                <p><strong>&#127881; Preparez-vous pour une experience inoubliable !</strong></p>
                <p style="margin-top: 8px;">Des artistes exceptionnels, une ambiance unique et des moments de partage vous attendent.</p>
              </div>

              <!-- Checklist -->
              <div class="checklist-section">
                <h3 class="checklist-title">&#9989; Checklist avant le festival</h3>
                <ul class="checklist">
                  <li>Telecharger vos billets sur l'application</li>
                  <li>Recharger votre solde cashless</li>
                  <li>Verifier les horaires de passage des artistes</li>
                  <li>Preparer votre itineraire jusqu'au site</li>
                  <li>Consulter la meteo et preparer vos affaires</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{ticketsUrl}}" class="button">Voir mes billets</a>
                <a href="{{festivalUrl}}" class="button button-secondary">Infos du festival</a>
              </div>

              <div class="divider"></div>

              <div class="info-box">
                <p><strong>Besoin d'informations ?</strong></p>
                <p style="margin-top: 8px;">Retrouvez toutes les informations pratiques (plan du site, acces, restauration, etc.) sur la page du festival ou dans l'application.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <div class="email-footer">
              <p>Besoin d'aide ? Contactez-nous a <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
              <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} Festival App. Tous droits reserves.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
